snippet.title: The Witch of Fern Island - Release Date Announcement
snippet.description:
🧙‍♀️ Become a Witch and immerse yourself in cozy life on Fern Island. 
✨ Master magical craft, explore the mysterious lands, uncover deepest secrets and join the community.

#TheWitchofFernIsland arrives on February 27, 2024.

🍏 Gatherer’s heaven
🐔 Cozy farming and life simulator
🔮 Emotional and compelling story

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1550010/The_Witch_of_Fern_Island/
Epic Store: https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/the-witch-of-fern-island-18df35
GOG: https://www.gog.com/en/game/the_witch_of_fern_island

💬 Talk to us on Discord! -   https://discord.gg/CrD575NJ9r  
💬 Facebook -   https://www.facebook.com/enjoystudiosa
💬 X -   https://twitter.com/EnjoyStudioSA
💬 Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/enjoystudiosa/
